creator: Juanma Altamirano
descriptionHtml:
Test your friends and your mental agility. Start a game with friends, family or new opponents to form words, create operations and train the mind. Get fun avatars by completing challenges and follow your progress until you master words and numbers.

King of words or Master of numbers! Download the application, start a game and may the best nerd win!

WORDS ROUND
► Form up to 3 words using some of the available letters and get points for each letter ... as long as the word is correct, if not, they will be negative points.

NUMBERS ROUND
► Perform basic operations (+, -, ×, ÷) to reach the target number. Or get a close number, because you will earn points based on distance.

CREATE A GAME
► That is the first step. Challenge your friends and family members who love puzzle games to play a game, or use smart search to find your ideal rival.

SOLO CHALLENGES
► Play different game modes and improve your skills to reach the highest positions in daily and weekly challenges.

AVATARS AND ACHIEVEMENTS
► Unlock achievements and claim your coins to get one of the fun avatars. There are 123 different kinds to collect, find your favourite!

PLAY IN 3 LANGUAGES
► Choose your language and play in English, Spanish and French.

Play one of the most fun, social puzzles on mobile! Download Brainito - Words and Numbers today!
descriptionShort: Build words and make operations! Smart is the new sexy! 🧠

- Slightly modify the scores for the Letter Rounds (Words of 9/10 are worth more)

- Modify the seconds you gain in Resistance
- Modify the speed bonus you earn in Superpoints
- Add a small icon to the Target Number in Number rounds
- The share button already works well in multiplayer
- Other fixes
